     <h1>Meet Our Staff</h1> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/reed-sheard.jpg" alt="Reed Sheard" width="76" height="90"> 
      <p><strong>Reed Sheard</strong>, <em>Vice President for College Advancement and Chief Information Officer</em>, joined Westmont in October 2008. He comes from Spring Arbor University in Michigan where he served as vice president and CIO for five years. <a href="reed-sheard.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/steve-baker.jpg" alt="Steve Baker" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Stephen Baker</strong>, <em>Associate Vice President for College Advancement</em>, has been in the Development/Advancement field for 26 years. He spent three years directing and managing capital campaigns for Community Counseling Service, an international fundraising <a href="steve-baker.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/sandi-white.jpg" alt="Sandi White" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Sandi White</strong>, <em>Assistant Vice President of College Advancement</em>, joined the Westmont team in October, 2008. Coming from a background in psychology, education and non-profit fundraising, she enjoys being able to combine these environments into one job. <a href="sandi-white.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/alex-nizet.jpg" alt="Alex Nizet" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Alex Nizet</strong>, <em>Senior Director of Development</em>, received a B.A. in Philosophy at UC Berkeley and a J.D. from McGeorge School of Law. A licensed attorney in California, Alex went on to receive his Master of Divinity from Yale University. <a href="alex-nizet.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/annette-richards.jpg" alt="Annette Richards" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Annette Richards</strong>, <em>Regional Director of Development</em>, joined Westmont in January of 2008. She is based in Newport Beach and represents the college in both Orange and San Diego Counties. Annette has a B.A. in Economics and Business from Westmont. <a href="annette-richards.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/joy-johnson.jpg" alt="Joy Johnson" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Joy Johnson</strong>, <em>Administrative Assistant</em>, joined Westmont in 2003, with many years of administrative assistant experience at Procter &amp; Gamble. Joy provides wonderful support for the Associate Vice President of College Advancement and the Senior Development Director as well as the <a href="joy-johnson.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/karen-sloan.jpg" alt="Karen Sloan" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Karen Sloan</strong>, <em>Administrative Assistant</em>, joined the Office of College Advancement in March 2010, as assistant to Vice President Reed Sheard. She began working at Westmont in April 2007, as the assistant to the Vice President of Administration and Planning as well as part <a href="karen-sloan.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <hr> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/trina-hudson.jpg" alt="Trina Hudson" width="76" height="90"> 
      <p><strong>Trina Hudson</strong>, <em>Director of Annual Giving</em>, has been associated with Westmont for over 35 years. The daughter of an alum and an alumna herself, Trina brings a deep understanding and appreciation for Westmont, its history and heritage. <a href="trina-hudson.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/james-byron.jpg" alt="James Byron" width="76" height="90"> 
      <p><strong>James Byron</strong>, <em>Assistant Director of Annual Giving</em>, joined the Office of College Advancement in 2009. His responsibilities at Westmont include stewarding the President's Associates and Class Agent programs. <a href="james-byron.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
