     <hr> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/kati-buehler.jpg" alt="Kati Buehler" width="76" height="90"> 
      <p><strong>Kati Buehler</strong>, <em>Senior Director of Gift Planning</em>, spent 15 years representing California agriculture in the State Capitol, and before then, 10 years as an investment advisor and certified financial planner <a href="kati-buehler.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/mona-wilds.jpg" alt="Mona Motte Wilds" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Mona Motte Wilds</strong>, <em>Director of Gift Planning</em>, works with Westmont supporters in Santa Barbara, in Los Angeles from Long Beach to Riverside and in California's Central Valley in Bakersfield and Fresno. Before joining Westmont <a href="mona-wilds.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/taylor-swan.jpg" alt="Taylor Swan" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Taylor Swan</strong>, <em>Gift Planning Assistant</em>, graduated from Point Loma Nazarene University (San Diego) where she earned her B.A. degree in managerial and organizational communication. She brings her skills in organization <a href="taylor-swan.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <hr> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/mary-dombek.jpg" alt="Mary Dombek" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Mary Dombek</strong>, <em>Director of Advancement Systems</em>, has worked in College Advancement for more than 20 years, and has overseen gift processing and all aspects of the alumni and advancement database since 1992. Mary holds a bachelor's degree <a href="mary-dombek.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/audra-pearce.jpg" alt="Julie Rubio" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Audra Pearce</strong>, <em>Advancement Services Assistant</em>, joined the College Advancement team as the gift processing specialist in 2009. Her responsibilities include processing donations, online gifts, recurring gifts <a href="audra-pearce.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
     <div class="member"> 
      <img src="images/bios/julie-rubio.jpg" alt="Julie Rubio" width="76" height="90">
      <p><strong>Julie Rubio</strong>, <em>Advancement Services Assistant</em>, has been in Advancement Services/Donor Relations since 2005. In her support role she assists the director of donor relations in the stewarding of named scholarships and donors. She also supports the director <a href="julie-rubio.html">[more]</a></p> 
     </div> 
